<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Delivered</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #7c3aed 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .header .icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            color: #374151;
        }

        .content p {
            margin: 0 0 16px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #1f2937;
        }

        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            background-color: #ede9fe;
            color: #5b21b6;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 16px 0;
        }

        .delivery-box {
            background-color: #f5f3ff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .delivery-box h3 {
            margin: 0 0 12px;
            color: #5b21b6;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .delivery-box p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .order-summary {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .order-summary h4 {
            margin: 0 0 16px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #1f2937;
        }

        .summary-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 8px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .summary-row .label {
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .summary-row .value {
            color: #1f2937;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .action-required {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .action-required h4 {
            margin: 0 0 8px;
            color: #92400e;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .action-required p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #78350f;
        }

        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }

        .review-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 16px 48px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #7c3aed 100%);
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 8px;
        }

        .secondary-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #7c3aed !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            border: 2px solid #7c3aed;
            margin: 8px;
        }

        .rating-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 24px 0;
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #faf5ff;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .rating-section h4 {
            margin: 0 0 12px;
            color: #5b21b6;
        }

        .stars {
            font-size: 32px;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 24px 30px;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin: 0 0 8px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #9ca3af;
        }

        .footer .brand {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #8b5cf6;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="icon">üéâ</div>
            <h1>Your Order Has Been Delivered!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p class="greeting">Hi<% if (locals.buyerUsername || locals.userName) { %>
                    <%= buyerUsername || userName %>
                        <% } %>,</p>
            <p>Great news! Your order has been delivered and is ready for your review.</p>

            <span class="status-badge">üì¶ Delivered</span>

            <div class="delivery-box">
                <h3>üéä Delivery Complete</h3>
                <p>The seller has submitted the final deliverables for your order.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="order-summary">
                <h4>Order Details</h4>
                <% if (locals.orderId) { %>
                    <div class="summary-row">
                        <span class="label">Order ID</span>
                        <span class="value">#<%= orderId %></span>
                    </div>
                    <% } %>
                        <% if (locals.serviceName || locals.gigTitle) { %>
                            <div class="summary-row">
                                <span class="label">Service</span>
                                <span class="value">
                                    <%= serviceName || gigTitle %>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                            <% } %>
                                <% if (locals.sellerUsername) { %>
                                    <div class="summary-row">
                                        <span class="label">Seller</span>
                                        <span class="value">
                                            <%= sellerUsername %>
                                        </span>
                                    </div>
                                    <% } %>
                                        <% if (locals.deliveredAt || locals.deliveryDate) { %>
                                            <div class="summary-row">
                                                <span class="label">Delivered On</span>
                                                <span class="value">
                                                    <%= deliveredAt || deliveryDate %>
                                                </span>
                                            </div>
                                            <% } %>
            </div>

            <div class="action-required">
                <h4>‚è∞ Action Required</h4>
                <p>Please review the delivered work within <strong>3 days</strong>. If you don't respond, the order will
                    be automatically marked as complete.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="rating-section">
                <h4>How was your experience?</h4>
                <div class="stars">‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê</div>
                <p>Your feedback helps sellers improve and helps other buyers make informed decisions.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="button-container">
                <% if (locals.orderLink) { %>
                    <a href="<%= orderLink %>" class="review-button">Review Delivery</a>
                    <% } %>
                        <% if (locals.revisionLink) { %>
                            <a href="<%= revisionLink %>" class="secondary-button">Request Revision</a>
                            <% } %>
            </div>

            <p>Thank you for using Jobber!</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br><strong>The Jobber Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>¬© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <span class="brand">Jobber</span>. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>Need help? <a href="#" style="color: #8b5cf6;">Contact Support</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>